{"tid":1647392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非入黎！ 要逐一瓦解警隊","createTime":"2019-10-11T17:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T17:37:00.000Z","uid":303992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3d60a260cea850f6e6d431da5c1681867ebe537e","tid":1647392,"uid":303992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"其實警隊入面一定有<span style=\"color: red;\">未黑化嘅警員</span>，亦都會有會好似王喜咁因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正義感</span></span>去當差，我地係要贏呢一場杖，雖然我地好嬲，嬲佢地<span style=\"color: gold;\">警黑合作</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">過分暴力</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">打死人</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">姦人</span>，但唔好再俾憤怒沖昏頭腦，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔好</span>要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">以偏蓋全</span>，有黑警唔代表全部人都係黑警，我地要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搵班未黑化嘅警察出黎</span></span>，唔好再無<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">差別攻擊佢地</span></span></span>，佢地都係人，俾人屌老母都會嬲會唔開心，我地要感化佢地俾佢地知有300萬香港人撐佢地企出黎，去瓦解呢個警隊！ 我地要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">針對</span></strong></span>嘅永遠都係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><strong><strong>黑化咗嘅警察</strong></strong></strong></span>！<br />\n<br />\n和理非。下次口號改做<br />\n<br />\n香港警察 保護市民<br />\n不徇私不枉法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港警察<br />\n不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人及忠誠、努力的態度行使職權</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h_Uy3SWpMNU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh_Uy3SWpMNU&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=3d6710da\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h_Uy3SWpMNU</a>"},{"pid":"9314f6cc7b33f9390c392d9fd0f6e5860eb2cbce","tid":1647392,"uid":303992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:22:48.000Z","msg":"上面YouTube 係香港警察嘅說話"},{"pid":"f46612412aae457dbbfa96302d00ba1c32aa1eb1","tid":1647392,"uid":3039